\par Using the command  \plain\f7\fs22 phrase=...\plain\f4\fs22   in the INI file, another file can be given this role. We recommend that you first copy PHRASE.A99 to a name of your choice and then implement this name in your INI file.
\par The phrases file must be in ASCII DOS characters. 
